    <p><ph keyref="product"/> includes a variety of built-in editor variables. You can also create
      your own <xref href="custom-editor-variables.dita#custom-editor-variables">custom editor
        variables</xref> by using the <xref
        href="preferences-custom-editor-variables.dita#preferences-custom-editor-variables"
          ><uicontrol>Custom Editor Variables</uicontrol> preferences page</xref>.</p>
